SUMMARY:Slamlandia - March
DESCRIPTION:Slamlandia is a poetry open mic and slam that meets every month at Literary Arts\, on the third Thursday. This mic provides a creative\, fun\, and welcoming space for all literary communities in Portland. We encourage poets new and old to come share their work. We strive towards a safe space for poets to read their own poetry\, witness others\, and participate in community. \nThis month\, Slamlandia will be hosted by special guest host Jennifer Nicole. The featured poet is Brian Stephen Ellis.
