SUMMARY:April Write-In: Poetry
DESCRIPTION:Join us at the Literary Arts Bookstore & Cafe for our monthly write-in. April is National Poetry Month\, so we are celebrating our poets! Whether you write poetry\, prose\, or something in between\, all stories welcome! \nOur Food and Beverage Assistant Manager\, Miah\, cooked up a new special\, the Sigh Swoon Sigh; a tangerine ginger latte topped with cinnamon\, complementing April showers\, or flowers. Hot or iced\, this drink will have you swooning. \n\nAbout write-ins:\nWrite-ins are community gatherings where writers come together to share space\, write\, and make connections. Whether you’re here to hit word count or make a new friend\, we’re here to support you!
